# H2O / STO-3G  STEOM-CCSD  (ALL-ELECTRON, to match the PySCF reference)
# Geometry = GANSU xyz/H2O.xyz (exact, Angstrom).
# Goal: extract (1) the STEOM ACTIVE-SPACE orbital list, (2) STEOM energies,
#       (3) the IP/EA-EOM eigenvalues ORCA used.
# Run:  orca orca_h2o_sto3g_steom_allelec.inp > allelec.out
! STEOM-CCSD STO-3G TightSCF NoFrozenCore
%mdci
  NRoots 3
  DoSTEOM   true
  OThresh   1e-3
  VThresh   1e-3
  PrintLevel 4
end
%maxcore 4000
*xyz 0 1
  O          0.000        0.000       0.127
  H          0.000        0.758      -0.509
  H          0.000      -0.758      -0.509
*
